Mandarin Translator
Responsibilities
Interpret between bilingual communications (Mandarin-Indonesia) for the appointed Indonesia Supplier.Auxiliary Chinese staff to develop new suppliers.Accompany Chinese staff  to do coal mine survey and pre-inspection before shipment (Kalimantan Timur or Kalimantan Selatan).Accompany Chinese staff to do loading supervision (Go to Mother Vessel ).Handling other logistical matters. Requirements: MaleMaximum age 35 years oldKalimantan locals (Kalimantan Timur or Kalimantan Selatan)Fresh graduate is welcome. Have internship experiences as interpreter / translator / active using mandarin language is an advantage.Required language: Mandarin, English, Bahasa Indonesia. Proficiency in mandarin is a must.Work location : Kalimantan Timur Dan Kalimantan Selatan Untuk informasi lebih lanjut silahkan masuk ke website kami diwww.hongfortune.com
